**Bottom line:** The stack is a **modern Next.js + React + TypeScript** app with **Tailwind/shadcn/Radix**, **optional Vercel Analytics**, **Stripe + Supabase** prepared for hosted Checkout flows, and **file-based JSON** for the **live kiosk and cashier API**. **`@stripe/react-stripe-js`**, **recharts**, **react-hook-form/zod**, and **next-themes** are in the toolchain for richer UI and future wiring; **user accounts** today are **browser-local only**, not a real backend auth system.